claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: A flow chart depicting subject participation in a study, showing numbers of subjects screened, randomized, assigned to groups, and included in safety populations (e.g., n=2344, n=2304). The image displays the study flow of subject enrollment and disposition; it does not present any data on antigenic match or comparisons to WHO- or FDA-selected flu strains, and therefore does not support the claim.
